Fork modifications
------------------

Modifications in this fork are licensed under the same terms (FSL-1.1-MIT,
with the same auto-conversion clause).

Substantive additions:

  - internal/ompclient/        — Go client for the omp coding-agent RPC
                                 mode (`omp --mode rpc`). Spawn/Call/Send/
                                 Close + event fan-out channels.
  - internal/workspace/omp_workspace.go(_test.go)
                               — implementation of Crush's
                                 workspace.Workspace interface backed by
                                 the omp RPC client.
  - internal/cmd/root.go       — modified to spawn `omp --mode rpc` by
                                 default; honours OMP_TUI_BACKEND for
                                 local backend overrides.

Module path
-----------

The Go module path was rewritten from `github.com/charmbracelet/crush`
to `github.com/fpcMotif/gosh-my-pi/apps/tui-go` so that:

  - `go install` does not collide with upstream Crush.
  - `go version -m` correctly attributes the binary.
  - Stack traces and pprof output cite the fork, not upstream.

When pulling upstream Crush updates via `git subtree pull --prefix=apps/tui-go`,
expect import-line conflicts. Resolve by replacing
`github.com/charmbracelet/crush` with `github.com/fpcMotif/gosh-my-pi/apps/tui-go`
in conflicting hunks.

